[Name] Qingy
[Summary] Qingy is a replacement for getty.
[Description] qingy is a replacement for getty. Written in C, it uses DirectFB to provide a fast, nice GUI without the overhead of the X Windows System. It allows the user to log in and start the session of his choice (text console, gnome, kde, wmaker, ...).
[License] GPL 2
[Homepage] https://qingy.sourceforge.net/
